episodes.title: Meet the Nuwaubian Cult Members from Eatonton, Georgia.
episodes.description:
A story about the emergence of a cult in Putnam County GA, followers of Dwight "Malaki" York who eventually went to prison. Produced by Rodney Hall, Andi Larner and Doug Richards, WAGA TV 1996 #nuwaubian
#cult #eatonton #Macon ga   #milledgeville
